Class IndexKey

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable

    public class IndexKey
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    This class implements keys for the indexFile which are basically the Seedname and julian date. It implements Comparable to support sorted lists.
